questionsAnswers.question: How do you stay updated with the latest technology trends?
questionsAnswers.answer: I regularly read tech blogs, attend webinars, and participate in online courses to stay updated with the latest trends.
questionsAnswers.comments: Felt confident answering this question as I actively engage in continuous learning.

questionsAnswers.question: Can you explain a time when you had to debug a complex issue?
questionsAnswers.answer: I once had to debug a performance issue in our application. I used profiling tools to identify bottlenecks and optimized the code, which improved performance by 30%.
questionsAnswers.comments: The interviewer seemed impressed with my systematic approach to debugging.

questionsAnswers.question: How do you handle conflicts within your team?
questionsAnswers.answer: I believe in open communication and addressing conflicts directly. I try to understand each team member's perspective and work towards a mutually agreeable solution.
questionsAnswers.comments: I felt comfortable answering this question as I have experience in team management.

selfAssessment: I think this interview went well. I was able to provide detailed answers and felt more relaxed compared to my previous interview.
coachAssessment: Jane showed improvement in her confidence and communication skills. She provided strong examples and demonstrated her commitment to continuous learning. She should continue to work on providing concise answers.
